<!subteam^S06HNNE4YQ0|@team> Great to see you all at All-Hands yesterday! :simple_smile: Slides are pinned here now, and a couple big reminders, so apologies for the long message:

*LEADS AND INTERNAL TRANSFER APPS, ALL DUE 11/2*
• <https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfmPh4_NBAK0YhAnM3WoIZNuj7YSHpb1x_VeVE_qHlZo8IIjw/viewform?usp=dialog|Apply to be a lead>! We are looking for 1 design lead, 2 business leads, 1 product lead, 2 dev leads, and 1 ops lead for next semester, and this is an amazing opportunity to give back to DTI. Reach out to any of us <!subteam^S01ACQLLWUW|@leadz> to learn more
    ◦ Nominate someone you think would be a great lead by DM'ing <!subteam^S03RJ149DTN|@ops-leadz> 
• <https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1OG4nVYawA4fGsFIFi1vtlb-rGMX9pCgsRgp74XyOgK8/edit|Apply to switch roles or subteams>! For PM-specific, please fill out <https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1lD-RU9nHs2WUhQPbW0_l_JKbGtZbBYjswJnGSuTd82I/edit|this form>.
*UPCOMING EVENTS*
• Big/Little Speed Dating today! 5pm at Hollister 368
• <https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1MSm-EwzywZYNk5KC9cbFKM_WKHc2ZpQj0QE21eLZGuY/edit?gid=613315046#gid=613315046|Sign up for TEC events> this week
    ◦ TCPL workshops, Fall Fundraiser baking and tabling :meow_party: 
• Our HALLOWEEN PARTY on 10/25. <https://partiful.com/e/u1KZPN6fVSWcH6Vpaspa|RSVP asap!>
See you guys soon :)
